---
description: Rules for payment, deep links, push, permissions, maps, and platform setup
globs:
  - lib/**/*.dart
  - android/**
  - ios/**
---

- Payment changes must preserve success, cancel, retry, timeout, and error flows.
- Never hardcode secrets, SDK keys, or merchant credentials.
- Route handling must be deterministic and idempotent for repeated deep-link opens.
- Platform integration changes must mention manifest/plist updates when required.
- Keep SDK initialization centralized; do not scatter setup across unrelated files.
- When touching notifications, verify app-open-from-notification behavior.
